OL,6,FSix popular wild swimming spots in
OL,7,Frivers across the UK could be granted
OL,8,Fofficial bathing water status this
OL,9,Fsummer, as part of a campaign to reduce
OL,10,Fthe presence of harmful bacteria in
OL,11,FBritain's inland waters.
OL,13,FWild swimmers across the country are
OL,14,Fcurrently plunging into rivers that
OL,15,Fcontain up to 20 times the safe level
OL,16,Fof harmful bacteria, in part due to the
OL,17,Fdumping of raw sewage in the water.
